      <title>印尼寻求保护纺织业免受中国商品冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/indonesia-is-preparing-ways-to-safeguard-local-textile-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼正准备征收关税并采取其他手段保护本国纺织业免受中国进口商品的冲击，这是一系列国家针对中国这一全球最大制造业国的商品大量涌入采取的应对措施之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/indonesia-is-preparing-ways-to-safeguard-local-textile-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 04:51:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
